div.p:
used_technologies
(dict): Technologies that can be used in assignment.

mapping_results
(dict): Result from proximity, coverage and demand analyses.

fiberpath_results
(dict): Result from fiber path analysis.

max_fiber_dist_km_per_poi
(dict): Maximum distance in km allowed for fiber connection, between POI and upstream node.

max_cell_dist_km_per_poi
(dict):
Maximum distance in km allowed for cellular connection, between POI and cell tower.

+
check_feasibility()
: check which technologies are feasible for each POI.

+
compute cost_per_poi()
: compute the unitary cost of connecting each POI with each technology.
+ assign_technology(scenario={lowest_cost, ranking})
+ get_results_table(): Produce table with summary of technology assignment.
